    "abstract": "<jats:p>We prove the folk theorem for discounted repeated games with anonymous random matching. We allow non\u2010uniform matching, include asymmetric payoffs, and place no restrictions on the stage game other than full dimensionality. No record\u2010keeping or communication devices\u2014including cheap talk communication and public randomization\u2014are necessary.</jats:p>",
